=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_LatoocarfianC_ex3 ===

DESCRIPTION: A neutral clean sound, with complex oscillator character around 1838 Hz, featuring very_slow attack and sustained envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, and filtered with steep_rolloff character.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: very_slow
  brightness: neutral
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: clean
  spectral_complexity_mean: moderate
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 1837.9174
  harmonic_decay_rate: -5.2825
  harmonic_regularity: 0.7183
  pitch_clarity: 24.8002
  inharmonicity: 0.0055
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -23.7680
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
